                     <interp inst="t18280529-244-off1341" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280529-244-cd1342" type="crimeDate">29th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-244-off1341 t18280529-244-cd1342"></join>, 1 box, value 6s.; 4 coats, value 7l.; 5 pairs of trousers, value 2l.; 10 shirts, value 50s.; 12 pairs of stockings, value 24s.; 12 handkerchiefs, value 1l., and 8 waistcoats, value 1l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280529-244-victim1322" type="victimName">
                  James 
                  Mackenzie
               <interp inst="t18280529-244-victim1322" type="surname" value="Mackenzie"></interp>
